## Running the System
Navigate to the API directory:
cd Source/api
Install dependencies:
npm install
Start the API service:
npm start
The API will run at:
http://localhost:3000
Example health endpoint:
http://localhost:3000/health

## Running Tests
Navigate to the project directory and run:
npm test
This executes automated tests validating the API endpoints.

